  "logNo": "223084344490",
  "title": "좋은 UI 디자인의 5가지 규칙(정렬, 여백 편)... 여러분의 사이트를 점검하세요.",
  "addDate": "2023. 4. 26.",
  "categoryNo": "76",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223084344490",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ead084f7-6d87-411e-9ba1-34bfbfb6b233\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a885c271-1024-4b60-9786-87259d96a2ec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9fc396d8-24a7-469b-9e01-c2efea72cf23\" style=\"\"><b>여러분 회사의 어떤 디자인도 이 규칙을 벗어나 디자인이 되었다면 지금 바로 수정을 요청하세요!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5da2dc54-6cee-4d36-9a8c-494b4a47e2e1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d004596-90d0-4b75-905f-436a33ab363a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08bf514b-a238-47a6-afd4-a4f97dee6c92\" style=\"color:#555555;\">앞에서 균형에 대해 이야기했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1429950-7cba-4a1b-ad0d-edb26ae929d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9436baf-74ef-483d-b66b-7a268d97c07b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c739572-fc14-4e83-bf88-32374d906372\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f93fa99f-f2c4-4d3b-9a4f-eb6c3718432e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">링크 삽입</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0391a6ec-2fad-4805-9bf6-2e312678aefa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ddde62b-b0b6-491d-b18c-482e0c77af52\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb90c288-1d66-4dd9-a410-73b6aedf6132\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-803bcf17-4b09-4a8e-b54d-a2cf29f6c2a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">균형, 즉 밸런스는 디자인에서 가장 중요한 요소에 해당됩니다. 특히 레이아웃 파트에서 가장 중요한 구도를 이루게 됩니다. 미술작품에서도 구도라는 개념이 있듯이 디자인도 균형이라는 요소가 존재합니다. 균형이 잘 잡힌 디자인이 UI를 떠나 UX에서도 빛을 발하는 경우가 많습니다. 특별한 경우가 아니라면 익숙한 대칭구조로 표현하십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a174bcd-88f8-42bb-9b34-7aad42a8e188\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-26bf233a-62cb-40f7-b53d-163891205191\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e39c94f9-2cd7-4014-8925-11ab6189a7c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cc53d3f-576a-484d-9288-0fc8d4bef246\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 정렬과 여백에 대해 이야기해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c608e36b-7c4c-459c-9799-f39e38cdc559\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c608e36b-7c4c-459c-9799-f39e38cdc559\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfNDEg/MDAxNjgxNTQ5MjI2NTcw.IDgWxagQPTXUuQUw0mgLZPVUEzd3_IESx8B4vIDYQs0g.oTSTB3s7aXClokzaJoB-AEs22ifPUrDkRsbcegkvgg0g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2481\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2599\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfNDEg/MDAxNjgxNTQ5MjI2NTcw.IDgWxagQPTXUuQUw0mgLZPVUEzd3_IESx8B4vIDYQs0g.oTSTB3s7aXClokzaJoB-AEs22ifPUrDkRsbcegkvgg0g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-d6315fd9-3e80-4159-a9e0-e97455494cf2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0700166e-4ae5-4979-ba0b-17cdc57de867\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMjI5/MDAxNjgxNTQ5Mjc0NTU1.gDXuR2jPMtNNw2iwCXV1TN9azjGJ-MZj6jHwYosI_Jog.Gxgy7DtNmdEmoEQ_M889A93j-UNCixxbf0v4TZkS-qcg.PNG.cookthedesign/Style.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMjI5/MDAxNjgxNTQ5Mjc0NTU1.gDXuR2jPMtNNw2iwCXV1TN9azjGJ-MZj6jHwYosI_Jog.Gxgy7DtNmdEmoEQ_M889A93j-UNCixxbf0v4TZkS-qcg.PNG.cookthedesign/Style.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32792f1b-2e5c-422e-aab3-752aa72cf58c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dd822663-9400-4e5e-8a7b-051ea0e951ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>정열의 스타일은 크게 4가지로 나뉩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6fdbae61-426f-4e58-8fee-c3ae92caac36\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54b9eab4-60cd-4884-b26c-2f37abb05d35\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정열은 특히 텍스트 개념에서 주로 설명이 됩니다. 정열은 좌측, 자운데, 우측, 양 끝으로 나뉠 수 있고 균등은 양 끝의 한 유형이라고 봐도 무방합니다. 이는 주로 문서에서 디자인할 때 어느 쪽에 기준을 두냐의 문제로 우리는 좌측 정렬에 익숙해 있다 보니 거의 모든 문서의 70~80%는 좌측 정렬이라고 봐도 무방합니다. 특히 편집 디자인이 아닌 앱 디자인 영역에서는 거의 3~4줄 이상의 문구는 좌측 정렬로 처리하는 것이 추세입니다. 이는 작은 모바일 화면에서 가독성의 문제이며 우측이나 가운데는 가독성을 해칠 염려가 있기 때문에 대부분의 경우 좌측이라고 생각하시면 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b08cf629-4916-447c-8807-03d5dcce8684\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:501px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b08cf629-4916-447c-8807-03d5dcce8684\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMjk2/MDAxNjgxNTQ5NTYxOTQw.RD112a5gJ1VTatJ-CF4_rhXTVTfNDlJ5kXWOyhvqN1wg.N6zcA4GeS33lOB48VWmy_UTMyqKO4y8SUTK_fHONI1wg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"501\", \"originalHeight\" : \"464\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMjk2/MDAxNjgxNTQ5NTYxOTQw.RD112a5gJ1VTatJ-CF4_rhXTVTfNDlJ5kXWOyhvqN1wg.N6zcA4GeS33lOB48VWmy_UTMyqKO4y8SUTK_fHONI1wg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d82be16e-26c2-4f4e-bb4a-d558dcb8fdf8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4f7689b3-3f26-4a1d-848b-a45ae767a7bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4f7689b3-3f26-4a1d-848b-a45ae767a7bb\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTUg/MDAxNjgxNTQ5OTkxMDQ3.oII2SCMa2lSeWo9Zpg124Ch3X6_DgvEdmHpaUMEEV30g.mZcEWMAuJmtOZWqSU0rgFVBVDRaEYzOXm_qHtEPGo40g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1302\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1124\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTUg/MDAxNjgxNTQ5OTkxMDQ3.oII2SCMa2lSeWo9Zpg124Ch3X6_DgvEdmHpaUMEEV30g.mZcEWMAuJmtOZWqSU0rgFVBVDRaEYzOXm_qHtEPGo40g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-56287e96-d8db-42b3-8267-2aaa1614e7b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-243ed4fb-b5b3-47ee-a229-1da2d4e1baec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8783b78b-04ae-434d-b246-44fed02422f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">좌측 정렬된 텍스트 레이아웃입니다. 거의 대부분의 디자인은 이 기준에서 작업이 됩니다. 이 좌측 정렬은 일단 읽기가 편하고 가독성이나 행간을 바로 찾아갈 수 있는 특징이 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c7532ba-378d-4b45-bce3-1676a119a4ef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3591655-5971-43e3-9667-1d431111eb8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6914fbd6-b714-420a-a8da-c294403cc5e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-192c1eaf-4438-44ae-9c55-5a65d390ab2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f5d0168e-f067-4372-9006-323938bf36e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f5d0168e-f067-4372-9006-323938bf36e8\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTIg/MDAxNjgxNTUwMDk0MTA2.Ag-MpsEDMzOsPrcL3SBkG1QQAag693-XyELuhDDu7oUg.Uo0jjXTh8J0R0LQSGgASMiQymJ5YFTzxUIHWpXqSx28g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1301\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1124\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTIg/MDAxNjgxNTUwMDk0MTA2.Ag-MpsEDMzOsPrcL3SBkG1QQAag693-XyELuhDDu7oUg.Uo0jjXTh8J0R0LQSGgASMiQymJ5YFTzxUIHWpXqSx28g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5601985b-53a5-4d67-a9d7-5a270686ec12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a3ffaa1-8db3-470d-8470-e2ccc45b9893\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-51e009fb-eac6-42ac-b457-7a53854155b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가운데 정렬은 일단 가독성이 좌측에 비해 약간은 떨어질 수 있으므로 줄이 4줄 이상이 되면 삼가시는 것이 좋습니다. 책자 등 편집 디자인에서는 크게 문제가 안될 수 있으나 디지털로 제작되는 웹디자인인 경우 가운데 정렬이 많이 단락을 이루면 가독성이 떨어져서 읽기가 힘들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcfd76e5-2925-48bd-831c-2fd4f04ca101\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44e5b79b-03d7-4469-a696-93a9cd5b2ef1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45565b2d-977e-47cb-b7c6-79af0178bc2a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-89f9e509-f3cf-4024-a573-c47bd49b81ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0b8090be-d4ce-4ac9-950d-dd4ee4d6b352\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0b8090be-d4ce-4ac9-950d-dd4ee4d6b352\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTIg/MDAxNjgxNTUwMjQzMTQ4.hNTRtonP7MW7hSIVGNKEH8VW6ZwrZ6rfkLOxl4mpwK0g.yTjNa16oTgVTmmKM2Mjtx9rPB2Apd0_OcYuj4U3MOgYg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1301\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1124\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTVfMTIg/MDAxNjgxNTUwMjQzMTQ4.hNTRtonP7MW7hSIVGNKEH8VW6ZwrZ6rfkLOxl4mpwK0